This three.js point-cloud engine is the shared engine of the viz ecosystem,
and projector is its home. Edit it here: every consumer (toaster, apairo_visu
studio) serves it from projector's install via `projector.web_engine_dir()`,
so one fix reaches every tool.

Consumers must not keep a private copy of these files. Historically the engine
was developed in toaster and re-copied here; it is now unified in projector.
